{"type":"message","id":"0ecaee73","parentId":"8e5cbfad","timestamp":"2026-03-19T15:34:25.598Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Thu 2026-03-19 23:34 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 请搜索以下4个领域的最新行业动态（2026年3月）：\n1. 企业数字化转型\n2. 智能安防\n3. 网络系统集成\n4. IT运维服务\n\n请整理3-5条最具价值的关键信息，返回格式化的摘要。"}],"timestamp":1773934465596}}
